                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">West</cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">  2 ½</cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">Ms to a willow point on the L. S   
                passed a Sand bar make-
                <lb/>ing out from the L. pt.</cell>
                     </row>
